('Smart Health Monitoring System', 'Comprehensive community health monitoring platform designed to detect and prevent water-borne diseases in rural India. Features real-time water quality sensors, AI-powered disease outbreak prediction, mobile health worker apps, and SMS-based early warning alerts. Integrates with ASHA workers and PHCs for rapid response. Targets 500+ villages with predictive analytics for cholera, typhoid, and dysentery outbreaks. Includes community health dashboards, automated water testing schedules, and government health system integration.', 'Arjun Sharma', '660eeca8-774d-42d0-a19a-f041038ead8d', 'HealthTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['IoT','AI','Python','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Arjun Sharma']),
('Smart Tourist Safety System', 'Next-generation tourist safety platform combining AI surveillance, geo-fencing, and blockchain-verified digital identity. Features include real-time location tracking, SOS emergency alerts with 2-minute response time, AI-powered threat detection in tourist zones, secure digital ID verification, multi-language support for 15+ languages, integration with local police and tourism departments, safe zone recommendations, and 24/7 tourist helpline. Blockchain ensures tamper-proof travel credentials and emergency contact information. Targets major tourist destinations across India with focus on solo travelers and foreign tourists.', 'Priya Patel', '660eeca8-774d-42d0-a19a-f041038ead8d', 'Travel & Tourism', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['AI','Blockchain','React','Node.js'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Priya Patel']),
('Cattle Breed Recognition', 'Advanced AI-powered cattle and buffalo breed identification system using computer vision and deep learning. Recognizes 50+ indigenous and exotic breeds with 95%+ accuracy from smartphone photos. Features include breed-specific care recommendations, genetic lineage tracking, health monitoring integration, breeding program optimization, and livestock insurance verification. Helps farmers access breed-specific government subsidies, connects with veterinary services, and provides market price information based on breed quality. Mobile-first design works offline in remote areas with cloud sync. Supports dairy farmers, livestock traders, and insurance companies.', 'Rahul Verma', '660eeca8-774d-42d0-a19a-f041038ead8d', 'Agriculture', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','TensorFlow','OpenCV'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Rahul Verma']),
('Disaster Education Platform', 'Interactive gamified learning platform teaching disaster preparedness and response to students across India. Features immersive simulation games for earthquakes, floods, cyclones, and fires with realistic scenarios. Includes AR-based evacuation drills, quiz competitions with leaderboards, certification programs, virtual reality disaster experiences, and teacher training modules. Aligned with NDMA guidelines and school curricula. Tracks student progress, conducts mock drills, and provides region-specific disaster training. Supports 10+ regional languages, works on low-bandwidth connections, and integrates with school management systems. Targets 10,000+ schools with goal of training 5 million students.', 'Ananya Singh', '660eeca8-774d-42d0-a19a-f041038ead8d', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','MongoDB'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Ananya Singh']),
('Smart Crop Advisory', 'Intelligent AI-driven crop advisory platform providing personalized farming recommendations to smallholder farmers. Analyzes soil health, weather patterns, market prices, and historical yield data to suggest optimal crops, planting schedules, and farming practices. Features include pest and disease prediction with image recognition, fertilizer optimization to reduce costs by 30%, irrigation scheduling based on soil moisture and weather forecasts, market linkage for better prices, and government scheme notifications. Voice-based interface in 12+ regional languages, works offline, and provides daily farming tips via SMS. Integrates with local mandis, weather APIs, and agricultural universities for research-backed advice.', 'Vikram Reddy', '660eeca8-774d-42d0-a19a-f041038ead8d', 'Agriculture', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Vikram Reddy']),
('Automated Attendance System', 'Contactless facial recognition-based attendance system designed for rural schools with limited infrastructure. Features include multi-student simultaneous recognition, works in low-light conditions, offline capability with cloud sync, parent SMS notifications, teacher dashboard with analytics, integration with mid-day meal tracking, and automatic report generation for government compliance. Reduces manual attendance time by 90%, prevents proxy attendance, tracks student attendance patterns to identify dropouts early, and generates insights on attendance trends. Battery-powered operation for areas with irregular electricity, supports 1000+ students per school, and provides real-time alerts for chronic absenteeism to enable intervention.', 'Neha Gupta', '0764ec52-9723-4d5e-8b31-c1743f8c94ea', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','OpenCV','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Neha Gupta']),
('Public Transport Tracker', 'Comprehensive real-time public transport tracking and management system for tier-2 and tier-3 cities. Features live bus/auto tracking with ETA predictions, route optimization using AI, digital ticketing with QR codes, passenger crowd density monitoring, driver behavior analytics, and women safety features with SOS buttons. Includes citizen feedback system, route planning with multi-modal transport options, offline maps, and integration with UPI payments. Provides transport department with operational analytics, fuel consumption tracking, maintenance scheduling, and revenue monitoring. Supports 500+ vehicles per city, reduces wait times by 40%, and improves route efficiency. Multi-language support and accessibility features for elderly and disabled passengers.', 'Aditya Kumar', '0764ec52-9723-4d5e-8b31-c1743f8c94ea', 'Transportation', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','GPS'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Aditya Kumar']),
('Waste Segregation Monitor', 'Smart IoT-enabled waste segregation monitoring and management system for urban waste collection. Features AI-powered image recognition to verify proper waste segregation at source, smart bins with fill-level sensors, automated collection route optimization, citizen reward system with points for proper segregation, and real-time monitoring dashboard for municipal corporations. Includes waste composition analytics, recycling rate tracking, carbon footprint calculation, and integration with waste-to-energy plants. Gamification encourages household participation with leaderboards and monthly prizes. Reduces contamination in recyclables by 60%, optimizes collection vehicle routes saving 30% fuel, and provides data-driven insights for waste management policy. Supports 100,000+ households with mobile app for waste collection schedules and segregation guidelines.', 'Kavya Nair', '0764ec52-9723-4d5e-8b31-c1743f8c94ea', 'Clean Tech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['IoT','Python','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Kavya Nair']),
('Smart Pesticide System', 'Precision agriculture system using AI and IoT for targeted pesticide application based on real-time crop infection analysis. Features drone-mounted multispectral cameras for disease detection, ML models identifying 50+ crop diseases with 92% accuracy, variable rate spraying technology, weather-based application scheduling, and soil health monitoring. Reduces pesticide usage by 70%, lowers costs by ₹15,000/acre, minimizes environmental impact, and improves crop yield by 25%. Includes farmer mobile app with disease alerts, treatment recommendations, spray logs for traceability, and integration with agricultural extension services. Supports organic farming with bio-pesticide recommendations, provides government compliance reports, and offers predictive analytics for pest outbreak prevention. Battery-operated for remote farms with solar charging capability.', 'Rohan Desai', '0764ec52-9723-4d5e-8b31-c1743f8c94ea', 'Agriculture', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['IoT','AI','Arduino'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Rohan Desai']),
('Alumni Management Platform', 'Comprehensive digital ecosystem connecting educational institutions with alumni for lifelong engagement and collaboration. Features include verified alumni directory with 50,000+ profiles, mentorship matching using AI algorithms, job portal with 10,000+ opportunities, fundraising and donation management with blockchain transparency, event management with virtual/hybrid capabilities, and alumni success story showcase. Includes batch-wise networking groups, skill-based communities, startup incubation support, and student-alumni connect programs. Provides institutions with analytics on alumni career progression, donation patterns, and engagement metrics. Features video conferencing for guest lectures, resource sharing library, and integration with LinkedIn for profile verification. Gamification with achievement badges, referral rewards, and annual alumni awards. Supports 500+ institutions with mobile apps and email campaign tools.', 'Ishita Joshi', '0764ec52-9723-4d5e-8b31-c1743f8c94ea', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','MongoDB'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Ishita Joshi']),
('AI Train Traffic Control', 'Revolutionary AI-powered railway traffic optimization system designed to maximize track section throughput and reduce delays across Indian Railways network. Features deep reinforcement learning for dynamic train scheduling, real-time conflict resolution, predictive maintenance integration, and multi-objective optimization balancing speed, safety, and energy efficiency. Analyzes 10,000+ data points per second including train positions, speeds, track conditions, and weather. Reduces average delays by 35%, increases section capacity by 25%, and saves ₹500 crore annually in operational costs. Includes simulation environment for testing scenarios, integration with existing signaling systems, automated rescheduling during disruptions, and passenger information system updates. Supports high-speed corridors, suburban networks, and freight operations with priority-based scheduling and safety-critical fail-safe mechanisms.', 'Sanjay Mehta', '052f09e4-3a5e-49f4-8a25-c5459ca46d36', 'Transportation', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','TensorFlow'], 'Seed', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Sanjay Mehta']),
('Panchakarma Management', 'Specialized digital platform for Ayurvedic Panchakarma therapy centers managing patient treatments, scheduling, and outcomes. Features include Prakriti assessment using AI-guided questionnaires, personalized therapy protocol generation based on dosha analysis, multi-day treatment scheduling with therapist allocation, herbal medicine inventory management, and diet plan customization. Tracks patient progress through 5-21 day treatment cycles, monitors vital parameters, manages pre-treatment Purvakarma and post-treatment Paschatkarma phases, and generates detailed treatment reports. Includes billing with insurance integration, patient feedback system, therapist performance analytics, and research data collection for clinical studies. Supports 100+ Panchakarma centers with telemedicine follow-ups, integration with AYUSH ministry databases, and multilingual patient education content. Ensures protocol compliance and quality standardization across facilities.', 'Divya Iyer', '052f09e4-3a5e-49f4-8a25-c5459ca46d36', 'HealthTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','MongoDB'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Divya Iyer']),
('Blockchain Herb Traceability', 'End-to-end blockchain-enabled supply chain traceability system for Ayurvedic medicinal herbs ensuring authenticity and quality. Tracks 500+ medicinal plants from cultivation to consumer with immutable records at each stage: farmer cultivation, harvesting, processing, quality testing, manufacturing, distribution, and retail. Features include QR code-based product verification, smart contracts for automated payments, quality certificate validation, organic certification tracking, and counterfeit detection. Integrates with FSSAI, AYUSH ministry standards, and GMP compliance requirements. Provides consumers with complete product journey transparency, farmers with fair price mechanisms, and manufacturers with quality assurance. Includes IoT sensors for storage condition monitoring, lab test result integration, batch recall management, and sustainability metrics tracking. Supports 10,000+ farmers, 500+ manufacturers, and protects ₹5,000 crore Ayurvedic industry from adulteration.', 'Karan Malhotra', '052f09e4-3a5e-49f4-8a25-c5459ca46d36', 'Blockchain', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Blockchain','React','Node.js'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Karan Malhotra']),
('Smart Classroom Scheduler', 'Intelligent AI-powered timetable generation system aligned with NEP 2020 guidelines for flexible, multidisciplinary education. Features automated scheduling considering teacher availability, room capacity, lab requirements, and student elective choices. Supports credit-based system, major-minor combinations, skill courses, and vocational training integration. Optimizes for minimal gaps, balanced workload distribution, and teacher preferences while ensuring zero conflicts. Includes semester planning, exam scheduling, substitute teacher allocation, and real-time timetable modifications. Generates personalized student timetables, faculty workload reports, and resource utilization analytics. Supports 50,000+ students across multiple departments with constraint satisfaction algorithms achieving 98% optimization. Features mobile app for students and teachers, integration with LMS, attendance systems, and automatic notification of changes. Reduces manual scheduling time from weeks to hours.', 'Sneha Rao', '052f09e4-3a5e-49f4-8a25-c5459ca46d36', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Sneha Rao']),
('Academic Authenticity Validator', 'Blockchain-powered credential verification platform eliminating degree fraud and enabling instant verification of academic credentials. Issues tamper-proof digital certificates for degrees, diplomas, marksheets, and skill certifications with unique blockchain IDs. Features include one-click verification for employers and universities, lifetime credential access for students, bulk verification APIs for recruitment platforms, and integration with 5,000+ educational institutions. Supports international credential recognition, micro-credentials for online courses, and skill badges. Includes student portfolio with all achievements, automated background verification for companies reducing verification time from 2 weeks to 2 minutes, and analytics on credential usage. Prevents fake degree rackets, reduces verification costs by 90%, and provides government with real-time education data. Compatible with Digilocker, APAAR ID, and international standards like Blockcerts.', 'Amit Kapoor', '052f09e4-3a5e-49f4-8a25-c5459ca46d36', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Blockchain','React','Node.js'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Amit Kapoor']),
('AI Crop Recommendation', 'Advanced machine learning platform providing data-driven crop recommendations optimizing yield and profitability for farmers. Analyzes 50+ parameters including soil NPK levels, pH, moisture, temperature, rainfall patterns, historical yield data, market prices, and crop rotation history. Features ensemble ML models (Random Forest, XGBoost, Neural Networks) achieving 94% prediction accuracy across 100+ crops. Provides season-wise recommendations, intercropping suggestions, risk assessment for each crop, expected yield predictions, and profit margin calculations. Includes soil testing integration, satellite imagery analysis for land assessment, climate change adaptation strategies, and water requirement estimation. Supports precision agriculture with field-level recommendations, government MSP integration, and market demand forecasting. Mobile app with voice input in 15 languages, works offline, and provides personalized farming calendar. Helps farmers increase income by 40% through optimal crop selection.', 'Pooja Bhatt', '75822b1e-e8d0-4f15-b9e7-a42a583c0b4e', 'Agriculture', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','ML','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Pooja Bhatt']),
('Civic Issue Reporter', 'Citizen-centric crowdsourced platform for reporting and tracking civic issues with government accountability mechanisms. Features geo-tagged issue reporting with photos/videos, AI-based automatic categorization into 20+ types (potholes, garbage, streetlights, water supply, etc.), priority assignment using severity algorithms, and automatic routing to relevant municipal departments. Includes real-time status tracking, estimated resolution time, citizen voting on issue priority, and community discussion forums. Provides municipal corporations with heatmaps of problem areas, department performance analytics, resource allocation optimization, and citizen satisfaction metrics. Features gamification with citizen reputation scores, monthly civic champion awards, and transparency through public dashboards showing resolution rates. Integrates with existing municipal complaint systems, supports 500+ cities, and has resolved 100,000+ issues with average resolution time reduced from 30 days to 7 days. Mobile app with offline reporting and multilingual support.', 'Manish Agarwal', '75822b1e-e8d0-4f15-b9e7-a42a583c0b4e', 'Clean Tech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','MongoDB'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Manish Agarwal']),
('Eco Tourism Platform', 'Comprehensive digital ecosystem promoting sustainable eco-tourism and cultural heritage experiences across India. Features curated eco-friendly destinations with carbon footprint tracking, homestay bookings with local communities, cultural experience packages, wildlife sanctuary permits, and responsible tourism guidelines. Includes AR-based heritage site exploration, virtual tours of 1000+ locations, local artisan marketplace, traditional cuisine discovery, and indigenous craft workshops. Provides tourists with personalized itineraries based on interests, real-time crowd management to prevent overtourism, and sustainability scores for accommodations. Supports 5,000+ local guides, 10,000+ homestays, and tribal communities with direct income generation. Features blockchain-based transparent revenue sharing, tourist education on cultural sensitivity, waste management tracking, and wildlife conservation contributions. Integrates with Ministry of Tourism, forest departments, and UNESCO sites. Mobile app works offline with downloaded maps and supports 20+ languages including tribal languages.', 'Riya Menon', '75822b1e-e8d0-4f15-b9e7-a42a583c0b4e', 'Travel & Tourism', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','MongoDB'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Riya Menon']),
('PM Internship Allocator', 'Intelligent AI-powered matching platform for PM Internship Scheme connecting 1 crore youth with quality internship opportunities. Features advanced matching algorithms considering student skills, interests, location preferences, company requirements, and diversity quotas. Analyzes resumes using NLP, assesses technical skills through integrated tests, and provides personalized internship recommendations. Includes company onboarding portal, automated interview scheduling, digital offer letters, stipend management with direct bank transfers, and attendance tracking. Provides students with skill gap analysis, pre-internship training modules, mentor matching, and performance evaluation dashboards. Features for companies include bulk intern management, project assignment tracking, and talent pipeline building. Ensures equitable distribution across sectors, geographies, and demographics with 33% reservation for women. Integrates with AICTE, NSDC, and Skill India platforms. Reduces placement time by 60% and ensures quality internships with government monitoring and grievance redressal.', 'Varun Chopra', '75822b1e-e8d0-4f15-b9e7-a42a583c0b4e', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Varun Chopra']),
('Microplastic Detector', 'Innovative IoT-based sensor network for real-time detection and quantification of microplastics in water bodies and soil. Features low-cost spectroscopy sensors, AI-powered particle classification identifying 10+ plastic types, automated sampling at multiple depths, and continuous monitoring with cloud data transmission. Detects particles as small as 1 micron with 90% accuracy, provides concentration measurements in parts per million, and generates contamination heatmaps. Includes mobile water testing units for rivers and lakes, integration with water treatment plants, and early warning system for drinking water sources. Provides environmental agencies with pollution trend analysis, source identification using polymer fingerprinting, and policy impact assessment. Features citizen science integration allowing public participation in data collection, educational dashboard showing microplastic impact on marine life, and research data sharing with universities. Deployed across 100+ water bodies, helps reduce microplastic pollution by 40% through targeted interventions, and supports India''s plastic waste management mission.', 'Tanvi Shah', '75822b1e-e8d0-4f15-b9e7-a42a583c0b4e', 'Clean Tech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['IoT','Python','Arduino'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Tanvi Shah']),
('Blue Carbon Registry', 'Comprehensive blockchain-enabled blue carbon registry with Measurement, Reporting, and Verification (MRV) system for coastal and marine ecosystems. Tracks carbon sequestration in mangroves, seagrass beds, and salt marshes across 7,500 km Indian coastline. Features satellite imagery integration for biomass estimation, IoT sensors for soil carbon monitoring, AI-powered change detection, and automated carbon credit calculation. Includes transparent carbon credit marketplace, smart contracts for trading, and verification by accredited third parties. Provides coastal communities with income from conservation, supports India''s net-zero targets by quantifying 10 million tonnes CO2 sequestration annually, and enables corporate ESG compliance. Features restoration project tracking, biodiversity co-benefits monitoring, and integration with international carbon registries. Includes mobile app for field data collection, drone survey integration, and scientific research collaboration portal. Prevents double-counting, ensures additionality, and provides real-time carbon stock monitoring for 1,000+ coastal sites.', 'Deepak Pillai', 'd456fb13-164f-496d-a1b7-9423f6b4a497', 'Blockchain', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Blockchain','React','Node.js'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Deepak Pillai']),
('Ocean Hazard Reporter', 'Real-time crowdsourced platform for reporting and predicting ocean hazards protecting coastal communities and maritime activities. Features citizen reporting of rip currents, jellyfish blooms, oil spills, marine debris, unusual waves, and water quality issues with geo-tagged photos. Includes AI-powered hazard verification, severity assessment, and automatic alert dissemination to nearby users within 5 km radius. Integrates with IMD for cyclone warnings, INCOIS for tsunami alerts, and Coast Guard for maritime safety. Provides fishermen with safe fishing zone recommendations, beach safety ratings for tourists, and shipping route hazard warnings. Features predictive analytics using historical data and oceanographic models, real-time hazard heatmaps, and emergency response coordination. Includes multilingual voice alerts, offline reporting capability, and integration with coastal disaster management authorities. Supports 10,000+ fishing villages, 500+ beaches, and has prevented 50+ maritime accidents. Mobile app with SOS button, weather forecasts, and tide information.', 'Shreya Bose', 'd456fb13-164f-496d-a1b7-9423f6b4a497', 'Disaster Management', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','AI'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Shreya Bose']),
('AI Crop Yield Predictor', 'Advanced AI-driven crop yield prediction platform providing accurate forecasts 3 months before harvest enabling better planning and risk management. Features deep learning models trained on 10 years of data analyzing satellite imagery, weather patterns, soil conditions, farming practices, and pest incidence. Achieves 92% prediction accuracy for 50+ crops with district-level and farm-level granularity. Provides farmers with yield estimates, quality predictions, optimal harvest timing, and market price forecasts for informed selling decisions. Includes what-if scenario analysis for different interventions, crop insurance premium optimization, and yield gap identification. Supports government with food security planning, buffer stock management, and import-export decisions. Features integration with crop cutting experiments, farmer surveys, and agricultural universities. Provides banks with credit risk assessment for agricultural loans, enables futures market price discovery, and helps FCI with procurement planning. Mobile app with personalized yield reports, improvement recommendations, and comparison with regional averages. Reduces post-harvest losses by 20% through better planning.', 'Nikhil Pandey', 'd456fb13-164f-496d-a1b7-9423f6b4a497', 'Agriculture', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','TensorFlow'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Nikhil Pandey']),
('Blockchain Supply Chain', 'End-to-end blockchain-powered supply chain transparency platform for agricultural produce ensuring fair prices and food safety. Tracks produce journey from farm to fork with immutable records at each stage: cultivation, harvesting, grading, transportation, wholesale, retail, and consumer. Features smart contracts for automated payments eliminating middlemen, quality certification at each node, temperature and humidity monitoring for perishables, and real-time location tracking. Provides farmers with 30% higher prices through direct market access, consumers with complete product traceability via QR codes, and retailers with inventory management. Includes organic certification verification, pesticide residue test results, and fair trade compliance. Features dynamic pricing based on quality and demand, automated insurance claims for crop damage, and integration with e-NAM, FPOs, and APMC markets. Supports 100,000+ farmers, reduces food wastage by 25% through better logistics, and prevents adulteration. Mobile app for all stakeholders with multilingual support and offline transaction capability with later sync.', 'Anjali Saxena', 'd456fb13-164f-496d-a1b7-9423f6b4a497', 'Agriculture', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Blockchain','React','Node.js'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Anjali Saxena']),
('Disaster Response Drone', 'Autonomous AI-powered drone swarm system for rapid disaster assessment and emergency response in remote and inaccessible areas. Features include autonomous navigation in GPS-denied environments, real-time aerial mapping of disaster zones, thermal imaging for survivor detection, AI-based damage assessment, and emergency supply delivery (medicines, food, communication devices). Swarm coordination enables coverage of 100 sq km in 2 hours, automatic obstacle avoidance, and resilient operation with individual drone failures. Includes live video streaming to command centers, two-way communication with survivors, and integration with NDRF operations. Provides first responders with 3D terrain maps, safe route identification, and resource requirement estimation within 30 minutes of deployment. Features night vision, weather-resistant design, 60-minute flight time, and automatic battery swap stations. Supports flood, earthquake, landslide, and forest fire scenarios. Reduces response time by 70%, saves lives through early detection, and enables data-driven rescue operations. Deployed across 50+ disaster-prone districts with 24/7 readiness.', 'Harsh Sinha', 'd456fb13-164f-496d-a1b7-9423f6b4a497', 'Robotics', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','ROS','AI'], 'Seed', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Harsh Sinha']),
('Rural Education Platform', 'Comprehensive gamified digital learning platform bridging educational gaps in rural India with engaging content and adaptive learning. Features interactive lessons for classes 1-12 aligned with NCERT curriculum, gamification with points, badges, and leaderboards, adaptive learning paths adjusting to student pace, and offline content access for low-connectivity areas. Includes video lessons in 15+ regional languages, AI-powered doubt resolution chatbot, peer learning communities, and virtual labs for science experiments. Provides teachers with classroom management tools, student progress analytics, and ready-to-use lesson plans. Features parental engagement through progress reports, scholarship opportunity alerts, and career guidance modules. Includes skill development courses, coding classes, and competitive exam preparation. Supports 50,000+ schools, 5 million students with personalized learning improving outcomes by 40%. Mobile-first design works on low-end smartphones, consumes minimal data, and syncs when online. Integrates with PM eVIDYA, DIKSHA, and SWAYAM platforms.', 'Meera Krishnan', '83d4cb8c-8e13-4b59-b48b-716df3d52b10', 'EdTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['React','Node.js','MongoDB'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Meera Krishnan']),
('Health Chatbot', 'Intelligent AI-powered multilingual health chatbot providing 24/7 medical information, symptom assessment, and disease awareness to underserved populations. Features conversational AI trained on medical literature answering 10,000+ health queries, symptom checker with triage recommendations, medication reminders, and appointment scheduling with nearby health facilities. Includes disease prevention tips, vaccination schedules, maternal and child health guidance, and mental health support. Provides information on government health schemes, nearest hospitals, blood banks, and ambulance services. Features voice interface in 20+ languages including dialects, works via SMS for feature phones, and integrates with WhatsApp for wider reach. Includes COVID-19 information, chronic disease management, first aid instructions, and nutrition advice. Handles 1 million queries monthly, reduces unnecessary hospital visits by 30%, and improves health literacy. Privacy-focused with encrypted conversations, HIPAA-compliant data handling, and integration with Ayushman Bharat and e-Sanjeevani telemedicine. Supports rural health workers with clinical decision support.', 'Abhishek Tiwari', '83d4cb8c-8e13-4b59-b48b-716df3d52b10', 'HealthTech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Abhishek Tiwari']),
('Smart Traffic Management', 'Comprehensive AI-driven intelligent traffic management system reducing urban congestion and improving road safety in Indian cities. Features real-time traffic flow analysis using 10,000+ cameras and sensors, adaptive traffic signal control optimizing green time based on vehicle density, incident detection with automatic alert to traffic police, and predictive congestion modeling. Includes smart parking guidance reducing search time by 60%, public transport priority lanes, emergency vehicle green corridor creation, and air quality-based traffic restrictions. Provides citizens with real-time traffic updates, optimal route suggestions saving 30 minutes daily, and public transport integration. Features violation detection (red light, wrong way, overspeeding) with automated challan generation, accident hotspot identification, and road maintenance need prediction. Includes traffic analytics dashboard for urban planners, simulation tools for infrastructure planning, and integration with Google Maps. Reduces congestion by 40%, cuts travel time by 25%, decreases accidents by 35%, and lowers emissions by 20%. Deployed across 100+ cities with scalable architecture.', 'Simran Kaur', '83d4cb8c-8e13-4b59-b48b-716df3d52b10', 'Transportation', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Python','AI','IoT'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Simran Kaur']),
('Renewable Energy Monitor', 'Advanced IoT-enabled monitoring and management platform for renewable energy microgrids in remote and rural areas. Features real-time monitoring of solar panels, wind turbines, battery storage, and diesel generators with performance analytics. Includes predictive maintenance using AI detecting faults 48 hours before failure, automated load balancing, demand forecasting, and optimal energy dispatch. Provides remote control capabilities, theft detection, and weather-based generation prediction. Features consumer-level smart meters with prepaid billing, usage analytics, and energy conservation tips. Includes peer-to-peer energy trading within microgrid, blockchain-based transparent billing, and mobile payment integration. Provides operators with grid stability monitoring, outage management, and financial analytics. Supports 1,000+ microgrids powering 500,000 households, increases renewable energy utilization by 35%, reduces diesel consumption by 60%, and cuts operational costs by 40%. Features mobile app for consumers and operators, integration with national grid for surplus sale, and carbon credit calculation. Enables 24/7 reliable electricity in off-grid areas.', 'Rajesh Kulkarni', '83d4cb8c-8e13-4b59-b48b-716df3d52b10', 'Clean Tech', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['IoT','Python','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Rajesh Kulkarni']),
('AR Heritage Platform', 'Immersive augmented reality platform for digital preservation and interactive exploration of India''s cultural heritage sites. Features AR reconstruction of 500+ historical monuments showing original glory, virtual time-travel experiences, and 3D holographic guides narrating history in 15+ languages. Includes gamified heritage trails, AR treasure hunts for children, and interactive storytelling with historical characters. Provides virtual museum tours, artifact examination with 360° views, and conservation status tracking. Features crowdsourced heritage documentation, AI-powered monument damage assessment, and restoration progress visualization. Includes educational modules for schools, virtual field trips, and integration with NCERT history curriculum. Supports tourism with AR navigation, nearby amenities information, and cultural event notifications. Features offline AR experiences with pre-downloaded content, accessibility features for visually impaired with audio descriptions, and social sharing of AR experiences. Preserves intangible heritage through AR performances of traditional arts, crafts, and rituals. Attracts 10 million users annually, increases heritage site footfall by 50%, and generates awareness among youth. Collaborates with ASI, UNESCO, and state tourism boards for authentic content.', 'Nisha Bansal', '83d4cb8c-8e13-4b59-b48b-716df3d52b10', 'AR/VR', 0, 1, 0, ARRAY['Unity','AR','React'], 'Free', 'Planning', CURRENT_DATE, ARRAY['Nisha Bansal']);
